00:10:51.980 --> 00:10:55.730 align:middle line:10%
Race, which is pretty
intense workouts.

00:10:55.730 --> 00:10:57.080 align:middle line:90%
And my back hurt.

00:10:57.080 --> 00:11:01.310 align:middle line:90%


00:11:01.310 --> 00:11:03.920 align:middle line:84%
So I called to make
an appointment for him

00:11:03.920 --> 00:11:06.020 align:middle line:90%
to see his regular doctor.

00:11:06.020 --> 00:11:09.890 align:middle line:84%
And from there, he went
for CAT scans and tests.

00:11:09.890 --> 00:11:13.430 align:middle line:10%
And the CAT scan showed that
he had lesions on his spine.

00:11:13.430 --> 00:11:17.320 align:middle line:90%


00:11:17.320 --> 00:11:20.230 align:middle line:84%
They had discovered it was
Methicillin-resistant staph.

00:11:20.230 --> 00:11:21.940 align:middle line:90%
So he was on vancomycin.

00:11:21.940 --> 00:11:24.010 align:middle line:84%
And it was an
emergency situation

00:11:24.010 --> 00:11:25.720 align:middle line:84%
to open him up and
