00:32:22.745 --> 00:32:26.230 align:middle line:84%
And what we know is that
about 80% of those antibiotics

00:32:26.230 --> 00:32:28.090 align:middle line:90%
are used non-therapeutically.

00:32:28.090 --> 00:32:30.869 align:middle line:84%
And they're used to make
the animals grow faster

00:32:30.869 --> 00:32:32.410 align:middle line:84%
and to prevent
diseases that may just

00:32:32.410 --> 00:32:34.535 align:middle line:84%
be occurring because of
the way we're raising them.

00:32:34.535 --> 00:32:37.663 align:middle line:90%
[MUSIC PLAYING]

00:32:37.663 --> 00:32:39.160 align:middle line:90%


00:32:39.160 --> 00:32:42.653 align:middle line:90%
[ENGINE ROARING]

00:32:42.653 --> 00:33:04.660 align:middle line:90%


00:33:04.660 --> 00:33:08.620 align:middle line:10%
>> It's as if someone said, what
would be the best way to come

00:33:08.620 --> 00:33:12.340 align:middle line:10%
