Let's feed them the same thing.

00:33:23.420 --> 00:33:26.290 align:middle line:84%
And let's just to sort
of ramp it up one-- let's

00:33:26.290 --> 00:33:29.420 align:middle line:84%
put daily small
doses of antibiotics.

00:33:29.420 --> 00:33:33.430 align:middle line:84%
So we're making sure to select
